    "description": "Word crack is a simple word guessing game. You have 5 attempts to guess the correct word, with each submission giving you clues and hints about what the word is.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863090/extras/80b329f213330403901f1a67a73eb2e2.apng?t=1741007311\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863090/extras/80b329f213330403901f1a67a73eb2e2.poster.avif?t=1741007311\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=76 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CASUAL</h2>No timers. No opponents. Just you and some words to crack. Customize the game how you want to play it, and crack words to your heart's content.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863090/extras/8c68a2d08f6b4fdc8530073a2a35e78a.poster.avif?t=1741007311\" width=614 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863090/extras/8c68a2d08f6b4fdc8530073a2a35e78a.webm?t=1741007311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863090/extras/8c68a2d08f6b4fdc8530073a2a35e78a.mp4?t=1741007311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMPETITIVE</h2>Test your skills against real opponents. See who gets the best score out of 5 words. Guesses are time based... try to not crack under the pressure!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863090/extras/caac681cbbbc93dad96b0af7a4378865.poster.avif?t=1741007311\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863090/extras/caac681cbbbc93dad96b0af7a4378865.webm?t=1741007311\" type=\"video/